songs.title: Done for Me (Loud Luxury Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Charlie Puth]
What you thinking?
You think that you could be better off with somebody new
(No, oh, oh, baby, no)
You say you're leaving
Well, if you wanna leave, there ain’t nobody stopping you
(No, oh, oh, baby, no)

[Pre-Chorus: Charlie Puth]
I won't beg for your love
Won't say, "Please"
I won’t fall to the ground on my knees
You know I've given this everything
Baby, honestly, baby, honestly

[Chorus: Charlie Puth]
I lied for you, baby
I'd die for you, baby
I've cried for you, baby
But tell me what you've done for me
For you, baby, and only you, baby
The things I do, baby
But tell me what you've done for me

[Post-Chorus: Charlie Puth]
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you've done for me
Tell me what you’ve done for me
Tell, tell me what you’ve done for me
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you’ve done for me
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you've done for me

[Chorus: Charlie Puth]
I lied for you, baby
I'd die for you, baby
I’ve cried for you, baby
But tell me what you've done for me
For you, baby, and only you, baby
The things I do, baby
But tell me what you've done for me

[Verse 2: Kehlani]
I never cheated (cheated)
Deleted everyone 'cause they made you uncomfortable
(No, oh, oh, baby, no)
These accusations (accusations)
I can't apologize for something that I didn't do
(No, oh, oh, baby, no)

[Pre-Chorus: Kehlani]
I won't beg for your love
Won't say, "Please"
I won't fall to the ground on my knees
You know I've given this everything
Baby, honestly, baby, honestly

[Chorus: Charlie Puth]
I lied for you, baby
I'd die for you, baby
I've cried for you, baby
But tell me what you've done for me
For you, baby, and only you, baby
The things I do, baby
But tell me what you've done for me

[Post-Chorus: Charlie Puth]
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you've done for me
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you've done for me
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you've done for me
Tell me what you've done for me
Tell, tell me what you've done for me

[Chorus: Charlie Puth & Kehlani]
I lied for you, baby
I'd die for you, baby
I've cried for you, baby
But tell me what you've done for me
For you, baby, and only you, baby
The things I do, baby
But tell me what you've done for me

[Outro: Charlie Puth]
Oh, tell me what you've done for me
Yeah, tell me what you've done for me
Oh, tell me what you've done for me
Yeah, tell me what you've done for me
